<title>JESUH CU SUNPAR PEK A SI CANG CH272</title>
<key>Eb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sunpar pek a si cang, Van Bawi thutdan cungah, Siangpahrang luchin a
 chinh, A hmaiah mithiang an kun.

[C1]
   Cu sunparnak pekmi, Khamh tu pawngah him in, Tu hnu ah,Tu hnu-ah, Tu
   hnu-ah, (Tu hnu ah, Tu hnu ah Kan lung a tling te lai, Tu hnu-ah)2.

[V2]
 Puanrang aih in an dir, Rel cawk lo mithiang hna, Tum-hnah kutput cio
 he, Upatnak pek in hla an sa.

[C2]
   Cu sunparnak pekmi, Khamh tu pawngah him in, Tu hnu ah,Tu hnu-ah, Tu
   hnu-ah, (Tu hnu ah, Tu hnu ah Kan lung a tling te lai, Tu hnu-ah)2.

[V3]
 Vawlei caah thlahmi, Tuufa hlawi in an sak, Tuufa thisen thawinak
 thawngin, Bawi luchin an i chinh.

[C3]
   Cu sunparnak pekmi, Khamh tu pawngah him in, Tu hnu ah,Tu hnu-ah, Tu
   hnu-ah, (Tu hnu ah, Tu hnu ah Kan lung a tling te lai, Tu hnu-ah)2.

[V4]
 Thiang Thlarau, na vel in, Lawmhnak cu na kan pek; Mithiang hna he um
 ti awk in, Vancung ah na kan hruai.

[C4]
   Cu sunparnak pekmi, Khamh tu pawngah him in, Tu hnu ah,Tu hnu-ah, Tu
   hnu-ah, (Tu hnu ah, Tu hnu ah Kan lung a tling te lai, Tu hnu-ah)2.</lyrics>
</song>